# Child Safety Standards Policy (CSAE)

At Vivah Sankalp, we are committed to maintaining a safe platform and have zero tolerance for child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE).

Our platform prohibits:

• Any content involving child sexual abuse or exploitation.
• Grooming, solicitation, or sexualization of minors.
• Sharing, storing, or distributing child sexual abuse material (CSAM).
• Any activity that endangers the safety or well-being of minors.

Reporting and Enforcement

Users can report content or profiles that violate our policies. Reported content is reviewed promptly, and accounts found to be in violation may be suspended or permanently removed.

Where required by law, Vivah Sankalp will cooperate with law enforcement authorities and relevant child protection organizations.

Age Requirements

Vivah Sankalp is intended only for adults who are legally eligible for marriage under applicable laws. Users must meet the minimum legal age requirements to create an account.

